## Limitations

This report is based on secondary sources and interpretations of historical events, which may vary in perspective. The lack of primary source analysis limits the depth of understanding of the internal dynamics of the League. Additionally, the report relies on the availability of online resources, which may not cover all aspects of the League's operations and challenges comprehensively. Further research, including primary documents from the League's archives, would provide a more detailed insight into its failures.